column9: Casana is changing the way healthcare does business with a smart toilet seat that enables effortless, integrated, and consistent in-home health monitoring. The Heart Seat™ captures key clinical measurements, including heart rate, blood pressure, and blood oxygenation, to assist medical teams with monitoring chronic conditions beyond the four walls of the hospital. The Heart Seat will be a FDA-cleared medical device focused on managing chronic conditions. The seat currently has three key sensors: 1. ECG (Electrocardiogram) - A single-lead ECG made up of two electrodes measure the electrical activity of the heart. 2. PPG (Photoplethysmogram)v- Red and infrared LEDs are embedded into the seat and function similar to a standard finger pulse oximeter measuring the local blood volume. 3. BCG (Ballistocardiogram) - Four sensitive weight sensors are embedded in the bumpers of the seat which measure the mechanical activity of the heart.

column9: Our mission at AI Squared is to be a global leader in AI integration providing increased adoption of AI, to impact organizations and lives. We value and believe in equitable access to AI where all people can adopt AI and have access to AI technology and insights regardless of their ethnicity, socio-economic status, educational or career level, work role, age, physical ability, or any other quality. The goal of our AI Squared technology is to level this playing field by providing AI integration technologies that would increase AI adoption and enable access to AI for anyone. This is our story. Dr. Benjamin Harvey was the Chief of Operations Data Science at NSA where he experienced challenges first-hand associated with the inability to adopt AI,  provide equitable access to AI, and unlock the value of AI for intelligence analysts and the military warfighter.  His inspiration came from his two brothers who were Army officers recently deployed to the Middle East (Kuwait, Iraq and Qatar) and SW Asia (Afghanistan and Pakistan) who both relied on intelligence to achieve mission. He began a journey and developed a solution to solve these inequities that simplifies and accelerates AI integration into applications ultimately protecting lives of Americans and military warfighters in similar situations as his brothers.   Our vision is to build the world’s most powerful model integration framework and AI integration software which enables any application to become AI-powered. For the first time ever data scientists can describe their models using our model integration framework and our AI integration software will overlay intelligence from inference results directly into a pre-existing web application.  We provide application developers with a software (e.g. SDK) and analysts with a no/low-code solution to customize the user experience

Any other website Simply click the Autobound icon to open “Autobound Anywhere”. Our algorithmic innovation has demonstrated how we can make Commodity x86 CPUs 15x or faster than most potent NVIDIA GPUs for training large neural networks. Investorplace considers the algorithm one of the biggest threats to NVIDIA Stock (a $500  billion company).  Engadget calls it a "Completely different approach to Deep Learning".  A quote from WCCFTech says, "If an implementation of this algorithm is mainstreamed it would almost instantly disrupt the dynamics of the deep learning ecosystem. Our innovation would not only benefit current AI training by shifting to lower-cost CPUs, but it should also allow the “unlocking” of AI training workloads on GPUs that were not previously feasible.

column9: Syntegra applies state-of-the-art machine learning models to create validated, synthetic data derivatives of health care data that match all of the statistical properties of the underlying data, but guaranteed to contain none of the original data, and cleared of privacy issues. Healthcare systems and data aggregators are forced to impose ever greater barriers to clinical data access. Syntegra is unique in developing a very large, open-access data platform of high quality, patient-level real-world data, trained using modern machine learning methods on health system information. Users can leverage our platform to conduct analytics, building predictive models, generating synthetic control groups for clinical trials and more. Since training is done on data at rest, and only deep learning model parameters are sent from the Syntegra API to the Syntegra servers, there is no risk of identifiable personal information leaving our secure platform. To satisfy health system security teams and end-users, numerous methods of validation, leak-testing and benchmarking are applied to the data derivatives before they pierce the health system’s firewall. Syntegra’s solution is scalable, and usable across many types of data, from images to financial information to sensor streams, will be securely added to our data lake over time. The company is led by a team of extraordinary serial entrepreneurs and university faculty with deep knowledge in medicine and data science.

column9: BeforeSunset is an AI-powered productivity tool to help teams and busy professionals with daily planning and time management. It offers various features to overcome the common challenges faced by businesses including; disorganized work, lack of focus, miscommunication, uncertain team morale, and inadequate planning. With AI power, it plans your day for you. We believe that to achieve success as a team, it's important for each individual to effectively plan their day and adhere to the plan. During the planning stage, 3 main questions need to be answered: “what do I need to work on?”, “how long will it take?” and, “how much time do I have?”.  Planning is important, but not enough by itself for success. Individuals need to maintain their focus throughout the execution of the plan. For ultimate focus, it is essential to minimize the distractions caused by unnecessary messages, switching between unfinished tasks, and losing track of time. With BeforeSunset’s workspace, you can plan your day by reviewing yesterday’s achievements, and unfinished tasks. You can stay on schedule throughout the day by keeping track of time for each task and focusing on one task at a time.  By tracking the time spent on each task, you can ensure that work is progressing as planned and make adjustments as needed. With analytics provided by BeforeSunset close your day by reviewing and reflecting on the progress you made. This detailed daily and weekly analysis can help you identify areas for improvement and plan your future work accordingly. Since work is not all we have, it is important to include personal planning in your day to make sure your daily plan is accurate. This doesn’t mean all your teammates see your personal todos on BeforeSunset. Our tool has the capability to make todos private if the user chooses. BeforeSunset's "Team Timeline" feature is designed for team members to share updates with the team such as; the task they're currently working on, their availability, meeting status, daily mood, whether they're working remotely or on-site, and who is currently working or taking time off. This helps keep everyone on the same page, prevent miscommunication, and minimize the need for additional communication. To sustain and improve productivity, reflection is provided by BeforeSunset’s analytics. These reports include information such as completed vs. unfinished tasks, meeting analytics, mood analytics, and how much effort the team spent on each tag.

column9: CAST AI is a cloud optimization platform that reduces cloud costs, optimizes DevOps, and automates disaster recovery. CAST AI's intelligent optimization engine delivers a cost-efficient, high-performing, and resilient infrastructure for every Kubernetes workload.  CAST AI brings resource and cost optimization to Kubernetes using an AI-driven optimization engine that applies cluster changes based on real-time workload conditions. It selects the most cost-effective instance types and bin-packs pods for maximum utilization. The platform uses spot instances that offer 70 to 90% discounts and are automatically selected for any stateless workloads. CAST AI also sets pod scaling parameters to achieve optimal application performance while maximizing cost savings. Moreover, users get detailed cost reports to enable forecasting expenses at the level of the project, cluster, namespace, and deployment, down to individual microservices. CAST AI provides an opinionated Kubernetes implementation that hides the infrastructure complexities with automation. So DevOps engineers no longer have to deal with IaaS complexity and can finally focus on higher-order cloud-native abstractions and concepts. They can create and manage CAST AI components through API, CLI, and Terraform to automate their infrastructure lifecycle management. CAST AI also provides services for in-cluster observability (logging, tracing, and metrics) and built-in security (encryption at rest and in transit). CAST AI protects workloads against downtime with a Disaster Avoidance strategy based on cloud neutrality and multi-cloud capabilities. To achieve 100% uptime, CAST AI adopts the active approach to Disaster Recovery by stretching applications and data across multiple clouds so that a cloud failure never becomes a disaster. Underlying all of our technology is a custom multi-cloud networking layer that makes the magic happen.

column9: SEED-STAGE • LOGISTICS TECH • FOR-PROFIT • SOCIAL PURPOSE CORPORATION. For buyers and sellers of perishable goods, Transparent Path creates real-time, end-to-end supply chain visibility technologies that reduce waste, cost, and risk.  WHO WE ARE: Former senior executives from the food, tech, and social impact sectors, from companies like Amazon, IBM, Xerox, Microsoft, Target, and General Mills. We came together in 2020 to use the skills we honed over long careers to create meaningful positive impacts. Our social mission: to keep food, medicines and other critical perishables out of landfills.  Founded as an LLC in 2018. Restructured and launched as a social purpose corp (C-corp) in 2020.  PROBLEM Supply chain data technologies have been underfunded for generations — still largely powered by paper, faxes and disconnected systems. These antiquated approaches were incapable of handling the enormous systemic strains caused by pandemic-related labor and equipment shortages, disruptions, and growing, complex regulation. Paper systems mean shippers and receivers can't manage what they can't see. So we decided to combine a number of advanced technologies and new approaches for today's challenges, including AI, IoT, 5G, printed electronics, and machine vision. SOLUTIONS We bring both software and hardware solutions to the market to reduce cost, waste, and risk in perishable supply chains.  -- PRODUCT 1: The Transparent Path Visibility Platform (PaaS). Customers affix our continuously-connected cellular sensors to pallets entering the supply chain. These sensors constantly capture and report the location, temperature, humidity, and other factors for these shipments into our visibility cloud. This platform was built with collaboration in mind. Supply chain partners are grouped in Consortiums — dynamic partnerships based around common trade relationships. Product customers are tracked, easing data sharing and showing who's "got the ball."  When location or conditions jeopardize our customers' products, we send out real-time alerts to the appropriate parties who can intervene and save the shipment, along with its freshness, safety, and financial value.  -- PRODUCT 2: FreshScore™ - our patented predictive freshness algorithm targeted at buyers. FreshScore uses both production data and supply chain environmental data to predict the freshness of perishables before they arrive at retail. This unique algorithm arms food producers with quality control data, allowing for the routing of the best product to the best customers, minimizing surprises and rejections. It also helps reduce waste by anticipating freshness and viability issues before they occur. We are partnering with ReFED, the top food waste non-profit, to bring this technology to market. -- PRODUCT 3: ProofScore™ - our "credit score for transparency." ProofScore is a patented algorithm that scores perishable producers and products based on data transparency. The more data shared with supply chain partners and consumers, the higher the ProofScore.  ProofScore puts information into the hands of consumers, answering the question, where did this product come from? How did it get to me? What happened to it along the way? ProofScore-ranked products can command higher margins and grow stronger customer satisfaction. We are partnering with a large Japanese multinational firm on its development.  -- PRODUCT 4: ProofTracker - our eco-friendly sensor device. This advanced temperature/humidity/shock tracker is a cellular gateway built on biodegradable materials.    BENEFITS Our products reduce customers' supply chain losses, retailer rejections, insurance premiums, wasted time, and labor costs spent on reconciliations. They also reduce negative impacts to natural capital, including keeping food and perishables out of landfills. Using our system, all supply chain partners know exactly what's happening to products in transit — reducing disputes while improving collaboration and trust. And customer relationships are maximized by the delivery of fresh, safe products at full margin.  CUSTOMER PROFILE Transparent Path technologies support food, pharmaceuticals, blood/plasma, transplant organs, and construction chemical shipments. The company also currently provides asset tracking for high-end hard goods.  PARTNERSHIPS Transparent Path has created partnerships with Intel, T-Mobile, Duke University, and ReFED. Intel has donated hardware, software, and ongoing counsel since 2020. We are working with Second Sun Laboratories to develop the most advanced hardware in the market, and with a large multinational Japanese tech manufacturer to develop ProofScore.  ACCELERATORS/INCUBATORS Over its short tenure, Transparent Path has been accepted into numerous accelerators, including 5G Open Innovation Lab, Microsoft for Startups, NewChip, and most recently, Plug and Play IoT.  FUNDRAISING To date, Transparent Path has been funded via bootstrapping, two RegCF raises, three grants, and four angel investors. In April 2023, the company was awarded grants totaling $440,000 from the National Science Foundation, ReFED, and the State of Washington. The company is building traction toward a Series A that will fund sales scaling and feature expansion.   FOR MORE INFORMATION Headquartered in the US, Transparent Path was founded by Eric Weaver, a 30-year enterprise transformation specialist. Prior to founding the company, Weaver launched the Xerox Customer Experience Practice, where he managed a $550M services book of business. His executive team includes senior leaders from Amazon, General Mills, Microsoft, Target, KraftHeinz, Xerox PARC, and the University of California at Berkeley.  Please visit transparentpath.com to learn more.

column9: Simbo AI, is a groundbreaking technology company providing Enterprise LLM AI platform for businesses for automations without human intervention. Simbo does not train its own LLMs but enriches existing LLMs of the choice with its proprietary Symbolic RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation) architecture.  Symbolic RAG is a perfect combination of LLM and symbolic knowledge bases for hallucination-free Gen AI platform for enterprise applications. As a specialized use case, Simbo is using its Gen AI platform for medical practice automation. It helps healthcare providers reduce burnout and costs, by automating mundane tasks using proprietary Lossless clinical NLU. Simbo AI is currently automating following use cases: - AI Medical Scribe as an API: Simbo sends patient conversation transcript to all well known LLMs from AWS, Azure, and open-source LLMs and uses proprietary clinical note ranking algorithm to identify the best clinical note. Our algorithm optimizes the cost as well to ensure it fits the budget. - Autonomous AI Phone triage bot: Triages the patients on inbound and outbound calls to autonomously resolve tasks. It helps reduce burden on healthcare staff and reduce cost for medical practice. Simbo has invented a groundbreaking concept known as 'Lossless NLU,' powered by our proprietary BISLU platform. Lossless NLU takes text or voice input and transforms it into a structured meaning representation called Thought Representations, without losing any part of the meaning. In contrast to prevailing NLU methods that primarily predict intent and entities, Lossless NLU retains the full context. We integrate Lossless NLU with Generative AI to eliminate hallucinations and perform fact checking. In the healthcare sector, where patient well-being is of utmost importance, the presence of hallucinations is unacceptable.

They will need to sign any asset to either prove that they own it, approve it, agree with it, or want to protect it. This could be any asset type - contracts, video, audio, designs, drawings, deeds, code and more. In an age of artificial intelligence and fake information it's more important than ever to validate the authenticity of any asset. We achieve this by enabling any file type to be checked, validated, signed and recorded on a blockchain thereby creating a tamperproof record. Everything that is created can be linked to the validated identity of the validators to prove it is true and original. What are the use cases for this? There are many - creating deeds of ownership, issuing stock or share certificates, carrying out due diligence, recording intellectual property, confirming that a video, photo or audio file is the true and original version, in fact creating a tamperproof record of any event or asset. Our second product, launching next month, takes this one step further. Once an asset is created it needs to be transferable, tradable and traceable. To solve this problem we have built a SuperNFT which is an asset linked to the validated identities of the creators or legal owners. Because the SuperNFT 'knows' who its owners are it is also a mechanism for collecting and disbursing monies to the rightful beneficiaries, and it does this Super-quickly. Our first foray is in the world of music to enable artists to create new experiences for their audiences and to enable artists to be paid more quickly and more accurately.

The name of our company is inspired by the bird species - Canaries. Canaries have been extensively used in research to study neurogenesis, or the birth of new neurons in the adult brain, and also for basic research in order to understand how songbirds encode and produce song. Thus, canaries have served as model species for discovering how the vertebrate brain learns, consolidates memories, and recalls coordinated motor movements.  This is a good analogy for Neural networks where backpropagation represents learning, final weights represent consolidated memories, and model inference represents recalling motor movements. column9: TieSet Inc. is taking the initiative in collective intelligence era as we believe it is wisdom that drives the future technologies not data itself. We lead the field of intelligence-centric platform with a distributed learning paradigm shift such as federated learning and create an intelligence-centric platform led by world-class research scientists and engineers. Today, cloud-based AI and big data systems face significant challenges but aren’t equipped to meet them head-on. Data privacy has emerged as a global concern, but AI systems utilizing big data simply can’t preserve privacy while learning. Similarly, in a world where IoT and device data outpace the speed of bandwidth growth, latency in AI data processing is causing avoidable bottlenecks.  TieSet has developed STADLE, a Scalable Traceable Adaptive Distributed Learning platform with a core feature of decentralized federated learning that preserves privacy while collecting and maximizing intelligence to be shared. Because intelligence is created and trained locally on edge devices to be gathered by STADLE, our platform generates high-quality intelligence without uploading data, enabling AI systems to operate and perform at scale while offline. Our message is simple. Collect, maximize and share the intelligence around the world. That is the world TieSet envisions for the next generation of technologies, for which we call the Internet of Intelligence (IoI) where intelligence is the one that is mainly exchanged over the Internet, not just raw private data. That said, AI is now transitioning from the product of big data to collective and continuous Intelligence, and can finally be productized in a variety of areas of our lives including finance, robotics, healthcare, automotive, education, public infrastructure, transportation, smart cities and energies, among a lot more others.

column9: Worddio is an AI-driven vocabulary-building app. We are growing our user base at a rapid pace because we offer our customers: - The unique feature to learn words without touching their smartphone. - 34 languages that cover 90% of the world's population. Our in-house AI/ML models help us in: - Building individual learning paths. - Optimizing marketing costs. - Deep user database segmentation (psychological, behavioral, and interests based) Customer Problem The main problem we face is the language barrier between peoples. This specifically applies to EU as a multi-lingual community. From other hand the biggest challenge for learning a foreign language is time. Advanced online technologies provide many learning opportunities but all of them require 100% focus for a long period of time which many people do not have. Products & Services To solve this problem, we turned the flashcards that students often use to memorize words into audio flashcards. Over 2000 people say that Worddio is a great tool for learning new words. With Worddio you can learn new words on the move or while doing something else, without touching your phone. Through this method, the learner will also memorize the pronunciation in the correct way, spoken by a native language speaker. We safe students time! Target Market The Worddio app is designed specifically for people learning a foreign language and who don't have time to learn and memorize new words. The Global Online Language Learning Market was valued at $12.49 billion in 2019 and is projected to reach $25.73 billion by 2027. With its 34 languages Worddio has potential usefulness for over 90% of the world population. Does it work? We have more than 200K installations and more than 1300 paying users. Business Model - subscriptions: 1, 3, 6 and 12 months, lifetime - up-sales of premium content - advanced flashcards by topics, Audiobooks and Podcasts. - Ads - general or targeted based on user profiles - Apply data & technology to other platforms/apps/fields . . . Developing a B2C model on a global level takes time and resources to break even, but once that happens, the return on investment is maximized at scale. Customer Segments Professionals: adults looking to improve their foreign-language skills for business or career reasons Casual learners: travelers, expats, or other persons wishing to learn a new language or enhance their current knowledge Sector-specific: Service workers, such as call-center staff or healthcare workers, who can perform better with a larger vocabulary and accurate pronunciation. Youth: 12-20 year-olds studying secondary languages in schools Sales & Marketing Strategy We have technology that allows us to build psychological profiles and predict users' behaviours without accessing their sensitive data. We can build bespoke learning paths, custom sales funnels, and target ads. The data gathered allow the pursue of three main objectives: optimzing marketing resources by leveraging predictive machine learning models creating individual learning paths based on users needs upsale of particular content or products Competitors The language learning apps space looks crowded but in fact there is a specific empty niche - passive learning. There are a lot of language learning apps on the market, but none of them use a passive learning method to save time for their users - Worddio is the only one that does. We are opening a new market group to support language learning. The Worddio app is a pseudo-passive learning app powered by AI which saves student time. Competitive Advantage Worddio main advantages are: - our app’s passive learning method  - huge stock of professionally recorded audio-flashcards in 34 languages. - scientific-based approach that leverages ML and AI to optimize costs and improve user experience - premium content section - AI features that will help us deliver the ultimate hands-free experience to our users.

column9: Hannah Systems’ mission is to deliver open and anonymous traffic data, never utilizing personal information, bringing focus to the most important tasks at hand, reducing emissions, improving congestion, and ultimately changing the way we live. Hannah Systems is making a difference in a progressive and socially beneficial way and we are emphasizing this objective by becoming a Public Benefit Corp. Hannah is a B2B software company that creates openness and the democratization of data, free from the location-based advertising business model.  The Hannah Systems AI was developed by a team of PhDs and traffic engineers and provides detailed intersection data, resulting in a more comprehensive view of the city leading to less time spent in traffic.  At Hannah Systems we enhance traffic data with AI technology and share this anonymous data via our open data platform. This enriched information enables analysis of traffic patterns and pedestrian activity, and reduces travel time, pollution, and congestion. Hannah Systems’ enhanced data can help cities redesign light phasing and surface new routes that can genuinely improve travel times. Traffic information is the catalyst that can bring about change, however, data has become increasingly more personalized and is a protected and proprietorial asset that it is not being utilized to help our cities. The Hannah Systems detailed traffic information makes travel more efficient, reducing the stress and anxiety of city driving, reducing emissions and making roads safer. The Hannah Systems open data platform is the foundation for companies looking to improve pedestrian safety, reduce emissions, streamline traffic and address the needs of the AV industry. Hannah Systems is partnering with cities around the globe in order to deliver the next generation of open, anonymous, and ethically managed traffic data. Hannah provides a deep understanding of congestion problems through advanced analytics, microsimulation of every intersection, a macro view of the overall city and the Hannah Systems’ Traffic AI.

Key Highlights of Our Offering: - Dedicated Focus: Tailored English language training for the healthcare sector, aiding immigrants in filling the job gap for Home Healthcare Aides. - B2B Model: Providing licenses to home healthcare agencies to upskill their workforce with crucial language competencies. - Competitive Pricing: Flexible license pricing between $8,000 and $25,000, designed to accommodate various agency sizes and budgets. - Innovative Technology: Utilizing VR and AI to deliver engaging, effective, and personalized language education. - Meaningful Impact: Aiming to enhance communication, increase caregiver confidence, and improve patient care standards. column9: Think of Sidekick Ai as your smart scheduling assistant. Our platform offers multiple ways to schedule meetings including; forward to schedule, link sharing and sidekick scheduling. We are the first scheduling software that uses machine learning to process language to schedule a meeting.  Forward to Schedule: When you receive an email, simply forward this email to your Sidekick. Sidekick will then read the email and try to find requested dates and time from the sender and match it with your schedule. If it missing information, it will reply back to the sender and coordinate the meeting for you.  Link Sharing: This is pretty standard in today's scheduling softwares. Simply share your scheduling link with someone and they will chat with your Sidekick to schedule the meeting with you.  Sidekick Scheduling:  Here is where more magic happens. Simply request that Sidekick schedule a meeting for you and it's done. Tell Sidekick who you want to meet with and when. From there, Sidekick will email the invitees and find times that work for everyone and get something scheduled for everyone. You don't have to worry about coordinating, following up or finding times... that is what Sidekick is for.  Sidekick also offers auto scheduling with your closest of contacts. We allow users to turn on auto scheduling for close contacts and when you want to schedule a meeting, it's instantly done and will be added to everyone's calendars.

column9: With Lodestar you can annotate video far faster than with any other available tools. Lodestar lets you drag and drop hours of video and start annotating right away. It continuously trains a custom AI as you label. The AI automatically predicts labels, greatly speeding up the work. As the AI gets more accurate, so do the labels, so the annotation team can generate more labels faster than ever. The custom AI also drives our active learning system that automatically finds objects buried in hours of video and queues up the frames for the team to check. It adds the most helpful frames to the top of the queue, so the dataset gains the most valuable data first, and the model gets better faster. Finally, integrated dataset management and data science tools allow data scientists to run experiments and validate the dataset by training inference models in parallel with the labeling effort. No wasted time and money creating labels that aren't adding value to the dataset. Today, training a computer vision model can take months of multiple cycles of labeling, exporting, training a model, analyzing the results, and starting again to achieve success. Lodestar changes all that. Our advanced platform for labeling and training with native video support trains a model in real time and allows your teams to work in parallel. You’ll finish in weeks what used to take months.

column9: If you have or are starting a business in 2021, most likely your business is designed around convenience. Most likely your business is going to bring your products and services to your customers doorstep. However, straight away you’re faced with a complex problem… should you develop an expensive software solution or, do you use what’s on the shelf and put the extra time and resources into growing your core business idea? Unfortunately, what’s on the shelf won’t give you a competitive advantage against the larger companies that have hand built their own solution. Without a custom solution you simply won’t be efficient enough to survive in the long term. This is where fieldd comes in! Fieldd powers your mobile services that travel to your customer’s home or work, and does so in a way that gives your customers the impression that you have hand built your own custom solution. Fieldd is different to other platforms because fieldd focuses on automating and prioritizing the customer experience. From the moment your customers book your services online, they are guided through a unique customer experience to turn them into a customer for life. Other platforms simply hold your customers’ details and often are no better than an address book. This unique “loop” to keep your customers engaged isn’t possible on other platforms and companies are forced to use a range of solutions to get the job done. Why hasn’t this been done before? Put simply, building fieldd has been a hard process! After 3 years of initial R&D & 30,000+ live R&D bookings, fieldd was launched in 2019 and now is the software of choice in 15 countries across 20 different industries. 15 years ago the thought of McDonald’s delivering your food was a futuristic thought. Today with the latest technology, UberEats has made this idea an everyday solution. 15 years ago the thought of catching a taxi was also not an everyday solution due to the inconvenience of booking, tracking & paying for your taxi. Yet today, technology has pushed taxis to become an everyday solution. The demand for customer convenience has always been on the rise and with COVID, this need has been supercharged even further. 100% of the time customers will instantly book the best priced, fastest service provider to come to them. Yet 98% of businesses rely on a 15 year old quote request form with a 1-5 day reply time. Before Uber entered the taxi & food industry, these two industries represented industries that were waiting to be optimized with technology. The amount of other service industries that are currently highly inconvenient and can be optimized, is practically endless. Prior to fieldd, the automation and customization within fieldd that are included with every plan, were only possible with custom software development. Now, it’s possible with a click of a button. Every day we are unlocking hidden potential in field service businesses globally, we look forward to seeing your business do the same.

column9: Blockchains are the most open, public and up-to-data data sources we have ever experienced. Data on blockchain though is extremely noisy, hard to read and even harder to make sense of them. Openstory was created in order to organize and democratize the access of blockchain data so users can make educated decisions, based on information and knowledge that before was only available to highly technical funds and companies. What’s happening on-chain Openstory is not a siloed API aggregator, a hand-picked catalog, or a centralized recommendation web2 service. Openstory is an indexer that focuses on scanning and unveiling on-chain truth like a story so everyone can easily make decisions based on objective information. What you see in the platform is not a recommendation from an employee or the curated information of APIs; instead, our database starts and ends with indexing the public on-chain information, offering a pure outcome of how people use and interact with web3. How challenging is this? Mapping web3 is both a data intelligence challenge and a UX challenge. How do we display the information meaningfully and drive usage beyond? How deep do we go? Your feedback is essential to its success, so we'd love you to be part of this journey early on. How to use Openstory The initial token/NFT sale can be the beginning of the experience, not the end. A creator or a brand can use Openstory to see how web3 users use/interact with their creations, spot their audience (who is buying and what’s their engagement) and reward them accordingly. A collector can use Openstory to assess if an NFT is worth buying based on usage/investors attracted, discover the up-and-coming collections, meet other collectors/soulmates, and create deeper relationships with the artists they love. A flipper can discover the most recent collections that grow exponentially. Everyone can check key market metrics, e.g., active users in the market, market growth, and marketplaces with the highest traction, so they have a better picture of the market they invest their money and time.

Even as an early stage startup, we walk the talk with women engineers making up more than 50% of our technical workforce.  The number of people in the US living with cognitive impairment (including Alzheimer’s Disease and related dementia) is over 5.8M today and is expected to increase to nearly 14M by 2050. The rapidly growing population of informal caregivers (more than 16M today) of people with cognitive impairment is subject to high stress due to patient behavioral symptoms, increased demands on caregiver time, and lack of adequate care-giving knowledge to address changing patient conditions. Caregivers face depleted income due to reduced productivity, higher use of health care services, decreased quality of life, higher burnout and risk of earlier mortality. The economic value of the caregivers' time spent providing more than 8.5 billion hours of care is estimated to be nearly $234 billion.   Amicus Brain’s AI-led services focus on caregivers and their patients before, during and after diagnosis, and while living with the disease, providing a scalable, cost-effective solution that reduces the caregiver load, raises the standard of current practices in neurodegenerative care and leads to improved health outcomes.

column9: Smoov is the first platform built to help couples automatically split and manage their shared expenses, before they have a shared bank account. Millions of couples are sending money back and forth every single day and money is the number one reason relationships fail. Today the process for splitting bills and expenses is manual, time consuming, and can be awkward or tense, plus no one likes doing math. Smoov makes it automatic, accurate and easy. While mirroring consumer behavior of sending money to each other via mobile. How? Smoov integrates with users' existing credit and debit cards and pulls transactions into a private running list.  This creates a very low barrier to entry and eliminates awkward conversations about signing up for a new card together - plus they don't want to do that anyway. Couples set up a default split % for all of their shared expenses that they can adjust on a per transaction basis if they want.  Users swipe which expenses they want to move from their private view to the couples shared view.  Smoov keeps track of the total damage (who owes who how much) and whenever the couple is ready, they can settle up via direct ACH transfer through Smoov. Why? Modern couples who value their financial autonomy are getting married later in life, with more independent wealth and studies show they are fully merging their respective finances less and less - in a world where timing is everything, Smoov fits perfectly into that macro trend among others.

column9: Geovea is a SaaS and AI-based web solution focused on simplifying travel discovery, planning, and booking processes for personal and business travelers, particularly those seeking local and unique experiences in North America. Geovea organizes travel in one place in the cloud, making it instantly searchable and available wherever the user goes. At the core, Geovea utilizes enhanced user map and route planning tools, allowing users to easily create simple or complex multi-destination trips. The platform also integrates industry-leading itinerary creation and calendar scheduling features to simplify any traveler’s trip experience.  One of its special offerings of Geovea is its Travel Chat AI. This AI-powered platform is revolutionizing the world of personalized travel planning by providing users with a fast and unparalleled experience in discovering and organizing their trips. Geovea Travel Chat AI allows users to easily tailor their search criteria at a city, state, or country level. It delivers personalized travel options in just 20 seconds, saving users time and effort and allowing them to discover hidden gems and off-the-beaten-path experiences. In summary, Geovea, through its mapping, itinerary, scheduling, and Travel Chat AI, is bringing a monumental shift in travel planning by enabling users to take complete control of their journey from start to finish. It allows for the exploration of exciting new destinations at unprecedented speeds, making the world of personalized travel more accessible and enjoyable. The bootstrapped startup company is based in Denver, Colorado, United States, and is now seeking its first round of seed funding to refine its platform and further leverage Geovea Travel Chat AI to provide the best user travel experience in the industry.

column9: Company Mission: At VersaQuant, our mission is to empower users with the knowledge and tools they need to excel in portfolio management. We are dedicated to leveraging cutting-edge AI and advanced quantitative techniques to simplify intelligent investing for everyone. Our Motto: Intelligent Investing Simplified Our Vision: We envision a world where individuals have the confidence and expertise to manage their portfolios effectively, all while significantly reducing the fees typically associated with traditional financial advisors. By harnessing the power of technology and AI, we aim to democratize financial expertise and make it accessible to all. Our Approach: We believe that the best way to achieve this vision is by providing users with intelligent bots that study the markets, understand market dynamics, and employ advanced simulations to assess risk comprehensively. Our bots are designed to communicate with users in a clear and structured manner, ensuring that they receive targeted responses tailored to their unique financial goals and portfolio. Our Value Proposition: Cost Savings: We are committed to helping users reduce financial advisory fees by up to 80% compared to traditional advisors. This means more of their hard-earned money stays invested and working for them. Performance Enhancement: Our AI-driven approach is not only cost-effective but also enhances portfolio performance. By leveraging technology, we provide data-driven insights and recommendations to help users make informed investment decisions. Key Features: Intelligent Bots: Our intelligent bots are at the heart of our service, analyzing market data, understanding user goals, and providing structured guidance. Market Expertise: We ensure that users have access to up-to-date market insights, enabling them to make informed choices. Risk Assessment: Through advanced simulations, we help users understand the risks associated with their investments and guide them towards risk-appropriate strategies. Personalized Interaction: Our LLM Agent understands each user's unique objectives and portfolio, ensuring that every response is highly relevant and tailored to their specific needs. At VersaQuant, we are committed to revolutionizing portfolio management through the power of AI and advanced quantitative techniques. Join us in the journey towards Intelligent Investing Simplified.

column9: One in four people in the world will be affected by mental or neurological disorders at some point in their lives. Around 450 million people currently suffer from such conditions, placing mental disorders among the leading causes of ill-health and disability worldwide; causing an estimated $450 billion worth of lost productivity. Treatments are available, but nearly two-thirds of people with a known mental disorder never seek help from a health professional. Stigma, discrimination and neglect prevent care and treatment from reaching people with mental disorders, says the World Health Organization (WHO). Where there is neglect, there is little or no understanding. Where there is no understanding, there is neglect. A new approach is needed - an integrated, multidimensional one. Enter Curis AI Inc. Curis AI Inc. is taking an integrated and innovative approach to mental health and wellness by using hybrid therapies consisting of virtual reality, sleep tracking, meditation and exercise. After a long day at work, everyone could use a little rest and relaxation. However, instead of heading home to veg out on the couch, imagine being teleported somewhere so tranquil and magical that your troubles simply melt away. Our vision is to enable everyone with a smartphone and or VR headset access evidence-based mental health therapy powered by virtual reality and artificial intelligence.

column9: ColentAI is an innovative HR technology startup revolutionizing the way professional achievements and skills are recognized, managed, and utilized in the modern workforce. At its core, ColentAI aims to address the global skills gap that poses a significant challenge to efficient talent management and recruitment processes. This gap is primarily a result of the job market's rapid evolution, which traditional recruitment models and tools struggle to keep up with, leading to inefficiencies and missed opportunities. The flagship product of ColentAI, the "Colent Passport," is a digital platform designed as a comprehensive and dynamic ledger of professional skills. Unlike traditional resumes, which offer a static and often incomplete picture of a candidate's abilities and experiences, the Colent Passport provides a living, verified profile that evolves with each user's career journey. It integrates data from various sources, including project contributions, skill assessments, peer endorsements, and real-time work performance, to create a more accurate and holistic view of an individual's professional capabilities. ColentAI's mission is to facilitate a more efficient and effective connection between job seekers and employers. By leveraging advanced AI algorithms and a user-friendly interface, the platform ensures that companies can identify and recruit talent that precisely matches their needs, reducing the time and cost associated with hiring processes. For professionals, the Colent Passport offers a powerful tool to showcase their skills and achievements in a way that is verifiable and relevant to potential employers, thus enhancing their visibility and employability in a competitive job market. Founded by experts in recruitment and technology, ColentAI is poised to transform the recruitment landscape. Through its innovative approach and commitment to bridging the skills gap, ColentAI is not just a product but a movement towards creating a more efficient, inclusive, and future-ready global workforce.

column9: The world is experiencing Data Overload and Insights are highly interpretive and time sensitive. Critical decisions cannot wait for manual analysis to create contextual meaning from insights, they need to be automated to deliver decision guidance and Augmented Outcomes for Companies, Executives and Shareholders. Decision Point AI™ is the company that has an Augmented Intelligence Platform that facilitates Decisive Impact for Companies, Executives and Shareholders. It utilises Decision Science instead of Data Science to focus corporate efforts on critical and Augmented Outcomes to deliver Decisive Impact to its clients. Decision Point AI™ is vertical and horizontal Market agnostic and is focused on technology and consultancy services for any industry or organisation. Our Augmented Intelligence Platform is already in use in Government decision making and Decision Point is currently engaging with a number of commercial clients on their specific business cases. Decision Science Data driven decision making augmented intelligence #dddm_ai "Decision Point AI™ augmented intelligence supports decision making when there is a lack of data to otherwise make decisions" While the standard pathway for Decision Science is to focus on data as a tool to make decisions and solve business problems. Decision Point has further augmented the current thinking by adding collated data through an augmented intelligence platform and applying human interpretive algorithms that enable expert context to establish both true meaning and trajectory in a real time manner. Real time DDDM through Decision Point AI™ dddm_ai establishes a clear competitive advantage in a world where enterprises are told competitive advantage no longer exists DDDM_AI is fundamentally different from the slower data science route which is involved in finding insights by analysis and modelling from data, after this data has been collected, processed and structured by data engineer. While business who are "driven most by data-based decision making had 4% higher productivity rates and 5-6% higher profits, a study of 179 large publicly traded firms" by Brynjolfsson, Hitt and Kim of MIT Center for Digital Business found in 2011 based on Data Science. No impact analysis currently exist for the evolutionary real time DDDM_AI that utilises augmented intelligence but by extrapolation the expectation is for higher productivity, utilisation and profits for client companies. Subjective Logic Augmented Intelligence A fundamental aspect of the human condition is that nobody can ever determine with absolute certainty whether a proposition about the world is true or false. The human capacity to create theories or hunches can have profound impact on the direction and effectiveness of organisations, enterprise and countries. Decision Point utilises an Augmented Intelligence Platform built on subjective logic to refine and explicitly emphasise the factors and certainties that underwrite decision options. Additionally the Decision Point Augmented Intelligence Platform utilises human insights as part of its data queries to augment the processing power of the AI with context and meaning of that data through human knowledge and expertise. Subjective logic is a type of probabilistic logic that combines the capacity of probability theory to handle uncertainty with the capacity of deductive logic to exploit structure of formal argument. Subjective logic explicitly takes uncertainty and source data trust into account. Subjective logic is suitable for modelling and analysing situations involving uncertainty and relatively unreliable sources. Subjective logic can be used for modelling and analysing trust networks where a measurement of the degree to which one social actor (an individual or a group) trusts another social actor and Bayesian networks that represents a set of variables and their conditional dependencies via a directed acyclic graph (DAG). Bayesian networks are ideal for taking an event that occurred and predicting the likelihood that any one of several possible known causes was the contributing factor. For example, a Bayesian network could represent the probabilistic relationships between diseases and symptoms.

column9: REALTIME PREDICTIVE INSIGHTS FOR HEDGE FUNDS: Simple answers to high-value questions. Investors seek fundamental insights into the companies they invest in. They can gain a competitive advantage by licensing proprietary information that only a limited number of funds can find and afford. To build these high-value datasets, we strategically place cameras/sensors to collect images/data of business activities that map to key company performance insights. We can process that data with AI (Computer Vision/Machine Learning) to generate unique insights into high-value questions for Hedge Funds and other asset managers.  Specifically, in our first two datasets we collect highly accurate and precise counts of every vehicle (Model Y or now Cybertruck) produced by Tesla at the GigaTexas factory and all four models (S, X, 3, and Y) vehicles produced at Fremont, CA. We license this data to hedge funds seeking an information advantage for trading equities.  Investors call this type of information Alternative Data or External Data because it's not published or directly sanctioned by the companies we observe. It is often built through innovative technology from unconventional sources. As we scale up, we expect to have numerous high-valued locations. We are hiring in several areas, DM me directly.

column9: In today’s world, data is getting larger and complicated to analyze. Almost every company is gathering a lot of data and is looking for professionals who can analyze that data in order to make predictions & generate insights. Companies like Tencent are employing several thousands of data scientists who are using data and building machine learning models in order to generate predictions & make smarter decisions. Unfortunately, the demand for data scientist exceeds the supply. According to McKinsey research, there will be a shortage of 1.25 million data scientists by 2024. Quality data scientists are hard to find and expensive to employ as a single quality data scientist costs about $117,000 per year according to Glassdoor research. The data scientist has to then spend 45% of their time on model building that we believe is a very repetitive & time consuming process. On top of that, organizations that are thinking about building an in-house solution require more than 3.5 million RMB in investment & usually more than 6 months of development.  That is why we’re building mltrons, which is predictive analytics in 5 clicks. We’re are enabling organizations to build and leverage advanced machine learning & deep learning algorithms without ever writing a single line of code or worrying about investing in infrastructure. The users just need to prepare the data and upload it into the application after which they need to tell the system what they want to predict. Then automatically, our AI engine builds the best fit model for their problems and provides them with real-time predictions and insights.  Our AI engine is built on a robust architecture with state of the art algorithms. Our goal is to get companies from raw data to actionable predictions in the fastest way possible. Mltrons Ai engine can be connected to various data sources after which it loads the data, prepares and cleans the data, build hundreds of thousands of combinations of algorithms and then selects the best model for the problem that can be easily deployed in one click, either by using REST API, uploading new data or using our visual prediction. In essence, mltrons is simple yet scalable. But most importantly, mltrons is accurate & intelligent because as more data is fed it, it gets smarter.

column9: Prophyles is reinventing Contact Management by pioneering a new category coined as Contacts-as-a-Service (CaaS).   Prophyles is solving the lingering problems in contact management related to data integrity, accuracy, synchronization, up-to-date, and privacy.  All current vendors, from low-end address books to high-end CRMs, use a centralized database which causes silos which are the main source of the problems.  Prophyles took a unique and contrarian approach by using a decentralized and distributed database in a peer-to-peer network in which profiles are connected using "Smart Contracts" in a blockchain - which is the core of our patent. Prophyles provides your entire digital footprint and those of your contacts, without ever compromising your or their privacy, and without ever being outdated since all Personal Information is constantly updated from the cloud onto your or their device, just like updates of mobile apps.  Prophyles offers you the most comprehensive and protected profile; reduces the probability of identity theft; connects you easily and safely with others through customizable digital cards that represent your different personas which prevent hackers, spammers, or even online predators from preying on your children; leverages your social network by capitalizing on the strength of your weak ties to get you qualified referrals; gets the latest scoop from social media about your contacts; finds people near you; records your daily events in a personalized diary; organizes your ideas in a customized journal; generates flavors of your resumes that are fed to job boards; completes online forms through AI-empowered APIs for you so that you don’t have to, etc. In short, Prophyles is your digital footprint in a truly connected and more secured new online world.

column9: Always know what's happening with your servers. IfMetrics monitor your Unix system with all running processes. When we find an error our state-of-art AI will automagically fix it. PROACTIVE IfMetrics is an AI-powered tool that monitors your Unix system in realtime. It comes with a state-of-art AI, which helps you detect problems and irregularities on your system. Unlike other monitoring tools IfMetrics will automagically fix problems that are deemed to be harmful to your server. It is able to self-learn using concepts of self-supervised machine learning. It gives you the power of fixing your system yourself without ever having to contact a support person or engineer. PREDICT HEALTH You can use IfMetrics to monitor daemon processes or similar programs running on localhost. IfMetrics is particularly useful for monitoring daemon processes, such as those started at system boot time from /etc/init/ For instance sendmail, sshd, apache and mysql. FILES, DIRS AND FILESYSTEMS You can also use IfMetrics to monitor files, directories and filesystems on localhost. IfMetrics can monitor these items for changes, such as timestamps changes, checksum changes or size changes. This is also useful for security reasons - you can monitor the md5 or sha1 checksum of files that should not change and get an alert or perform an action if they should change.

column9: Itoric has developed a linguistics-based platform on which it is building a system of general intelligence.  Its core is based in linguistics, enabling it to go where AI cannot readily go and do what AI cannot possibly do.  It skirts the current industry paradigm of creating software-based products whose logic is based on a human programmer's knowledge and ability.  We have dubbed this new realm 'Human-Like Intelligence' (HLI).  The HLI 'agent' is trained in English rather than with numbers and data.  For analysis and problem solving, it does not use scripted or programmed methods. For its enabling technology, Itoric has one patent issued, one pending and another in process . HLI contrasts with AI-based intelligent systems is that it quite accurately mimics human thinking.  Traditional situationally-dependent programming or scripting is not used, neither by Itoric nor the end customer.  HLI instead depends upon English-language teaching, back-stories, observations and situational briefings.  Itoric's HLI is Subject-Matter Expert (SME) trained, something for which no equivalent exits under the AI paradigms of the past 70 years.  For autonomous systems, the accuracy and completeness of an HLI's assessments and decisions are driven by the completeness of its text-based training.  Unlike programmed autonomous systems, performance does not depend on how accurately software requirements were defined or how insightful its programmers were. Beginning in 2013, the founder created new IP for a method of storing concepts and knowledge in a now-patented specific form of data graph.  Access to the HLI's gained knowledge is linguistics-based, and every neuron in it is self-describing, in English.  Its internal data graph design allows for rapid multi-dimensional accesses of concepts and knowledge.  With superior linguistic approaches, it understands every-day nuanced meanings and purpose for every word in a sentence or fragment of speech.  Concepts in its graph-like memory are learned, managed and updated primarily in ordinary English.  Training is text-based, created by subject-matter experts, whether dealing with how to walk or the implications of human action.  The enabling technology was its patented neuron structure that each represents a single concept.  With this, the creation of a robust English parser and related semantic analyzer were possible. The analysis of external text's emotional content is a natural byproduct of the HLI's semantic analyzer, as it the very concept of topic.  Both of these are difficult for conventional systems, as is the correct interpretation of colloquial idioms in context.  Here, they are natural outcomes flowing from the semantic analyzer. Many fundamental paradigms, tenants and methods of Artificial Intelligence (AI) are demonstrated to be self-limiting and self-perpetuating.  They have confined Artificial Intelligence to niches far removed from the original lofty dreams of a "general intelligence".  That is, AI cannot be applied almost anywhere human-like intelligence is needed, whereas Itoric's HLI system can be.  The timeframe for AI arriving at such an inflection of general intelligence remains 20 years distant, a prognostic delayed year over year. In its persistence, Itoric has overcome high barriers to entry for general intelligence, having solved intractable unbounded problems.  The HLI is *not* bio-mimetic.  Rather, the psycho-mimetic nature of the Visel Mind Model readily handles cultural idioms, regional culture, human values, political issues, and even the broken English that makes up today's (English) communication.  The initial target market for Itoric's HLI are the autonomous analysis of intelligence, finding its implications, and the control of systems where a human in the loop is not practical.  A general manager from one of the three-letter agencies disagreed with the founders assessment as to the HLI's market estimate of $200B.  He insisted that the more realistic estimate is $3T.  The founder has since come to ready agreement with that assessment. The development status of the HLI is currently Technology Readiness Level 5 or 6 (TRL 5 or TRL6) for the framework, parser and semantic analyzer.  The HLI's mind model  operates on low power and modest memory resources, not the estimated tera-flops needed for AI. Itoric will be seeking about $10M and about 18 months to deliver a first-generation product to the initial Intelligence or aerospace industries.

column9: SDS produces a machine learning tool for the financial services industry which dramatically reduces the cost of harvesting and cleaning data.   The company was founded in 2018 by a team of analysts and investment professionals who had formerly worked as part of a development group in a San Francisco angel capital office.  Previously, the team had been tasked with building various in-house data solutions, including one to supply structured XBRL financials to subsidiary Revere Data (later acquired by FACTSET).  It was through this experience that the basis of SDS as a standalone provider was born.   The lightbulb moment for the team came when it moved beyond standard financials (Income Statement/Balance Sheet/Cash Flow) and began mining esoteric tables buried in 10K/Qs, such as REIT FFO (Funds From Operations) for a hedge fund manager client.  Although outside of the ordinary workflow, SDS tools easily accomplished the task with a skeleton crew of staff and a microscopic budget (compared to incumbent data purveyors).  At that point, the decision was made to commercialize. Since 2018, SDS has been in stealth mode, quietly improving its semantic parsing engine and its user interface, while preparing for a public launch.  We intend to disrupt a well established and very static industry which currently relies mostly on manual processes to populate databases.  Through automation, our platform improves the efficiency of collecting, maintaining, and updating financial information by an order of magnitude.   SDS anticipates an initial release in Fall of 2020.

column9: AI and the future of Payment Technology Adroit Partners invests in merchant portfolios that can take advantage of future AI payment technology, like Computer and voice activated payments.  Computer-vision powered payments Utilizing AI in the payments space has streamlined the functionality of payment technology.  As more consumers shop online and via mobile, facial recognition has been a more recent technology that many see as the future of digital payments.  By using device-vision AI, credit and debit card data can be stored with your facial ID and used to make purchases.   Amazon’s Deeplens technology which enables cameras to check out your grocery items without going through a cashier is one example of this.  While it’s still in development, it’s set to disrupt payment systems. Voice-activated payments Biometric protected payments are now more mainstream as they integrate with most smartphones. But more advancements are aspiring to integrate AI powered smart assistants with voice-recognition technologies. With voice-activated payment technology, smart assistants access your accounts for the transaction. In the future, voice activated payments won’t be hinged on assistants or other biometric securities for verification. As effortless payment leads the way in the digital transformation of financial services,  it won’t take long before these displace the current methods used today.

column9: We are physicians who code, so that provides us with a unique perspective in building our platform. As practicing physicians, each day we see the limits and failings of existing EMR systems. Those systems have demonstrated that they are incapable of scale. They impose artificial patient capacity limits on physicians and represent a contributing source of physician burnout. As a result, healthcare has outgrown its current technology and patient care suffers.  Our mission is to change this with Artificial Intelligence. And with that, to create a paradigm shift in patient care, allowing physicians and healers to contribute knowledge and leverage the latest innovations in AI technology to develop an intelligent patient outcome feedback loop.  Our AI model has been specifically designed to accelerate the advancement of clinical therapies and expand the reach and impact of these advancements. This will permit medicine to bring to reality the dream of equity inpatient care by accruing and sharing physicians’ cumulative discoveries, knowledge, and experiences with every single patient encounter.
